window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b><i>Azaria </i></b><i>is a vampire.</i><br> Newly turned, she was taken and kept in a dark, cement room, hidden from the outside world, tortured and studied.</p> <p><b><i>Ian </i></b><i>is a businessman.</i><br> Ian Villari and the rest of his vampire family are well respected figureheads around town. When the Dietrich family extends the offer of their name and coven, Ian refuses, setting their allies on edge.</p> <p>Left alone in the house when her captor dies, Azaria works to acclimate to her new freedom. When Ian spots the curious vampire lurking around town, timid and nervous of her surroundings, he finds her intriguing. The only thing? This mysterious creature just might be what the Dietrich family needs to gain leverage over the Villari.</p> <p><b><i>Welcome to Pharos Hills.<br> A picturesque, little town on the Virginian east coast.<br> We invite you to share in all the beauty it has to offer.<br> And all the not so beautiful.<br> Because, after all…</i></b></p> <p><b><i>When you live amongst monsters,<br> you’re bound to find ardent desire.</i></b></p>"; 
